name: Turned On Tech 05 - Electric Toothbrush
description: A fun series exploring the lascivious side of technology. Everyone loves to use the latest tech, but this series of work focusses on how the tech likes to be used. Sure, it'll clean your teeth but it'll also make you gag if you let it! (copyright) Alternative Aesthetics. For personal non-commercial use only. Find me on Instagram and Twitter @alt_aesthetics
